MinistryHealthDB/
├── Code.sql                     # Main SQL script for database schema and sample data
├── .gitignore                   # Specifies files to ignore in version control
├── README.md                    # Project overview and usage instructions
├── LICENSE                      # License information for the repository
├── CONTRIBUTING.md              # Guidelines for contributing to the project
├── CHANGELOG.md                 # (Optional) Tracks changes made to the project
├── docs/                        # Documentation files
│   ├── setup.md                 # Instructions for setting up the project
│   ├── database_design.md       # Detailed explanation of the database design
├── diagrams/                    # Folder for design and architectural diagrams
│   └── Government Health System EER Diagram.pdf  # EER diagram of the database
├── example_data/                # Folder for example data and database dumps
│   └── sample_data.sql          # Example SQL data for testing
└── tests/                       # Folder for testing and validation scripts
    └── validation_queries.sql   # SQL scripts for validating database integrity